com.streakapi.crm.api

Interface IStreakURIBuilderUtil

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StreakURIBuilderUtilImpl

    public interface IStreakURIBuilderUtil
    Generates the URI for various Streak queries. All values returned are full URIs of the form https://www.streak.com/api/v1/{queryDependent}
    Author:
    dineshkp
    See Also:
    https://www.streak.com/api
